latestPosts.caption:
As someone named Nandini, I feel a special connection to the divine energy of Goddess Parvati during Navratri.

 “Nandini” is the manifestation of abundance and nurturing love, which inspires me to embrace these qualities in my own life. 

This sacred time reminds me of the strength, grace, and blessings that the goddess bestows upon us. Wishing everyone a prosperous and harmonious Navratri filled with divine energy. 🕉️ 

#Navratri #GoddessWithin #DivineBlessings

5 year old nini would never believe that THE DAY is here✨🤍 

🎥 : @hexareelstudios 

#arangetram #dance

After 20 years of dancing, countless hurdles, and a pandemic that delayed this dream, my Arangetram is finally complete🥰

I am beyond grateful to my incredible parents for their unwavering support and to everyone who came out to cheer me on🙌

This moment was made so special because of you all, and I can’t wait to share more about my unforgettable day!🤍

#arangetram #dancer

posting this before I get in my head & decide not to!!
